---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Quaid Evals"
  description="About the Quaid benchmark site and why the project publishes results."
>
  <div class="page">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="page-kicker">About</div>
      <h1>Quaid Evals</h1>
      <p>Benchmark pages for a local-first memory system.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="split-grid">
      <div class="panel">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <h2>What This Is</h2>
        </div>
        <ul class="content-list">
          <li>Quaid is local-first agent memory with an MCP server and no cloud dependency.</li>
          <li>Results are published for transparency so anyone can reproduce the numbers.</li>
          <li>Every release runs through GitHub Actions before scores land on the site.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="panel">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <h2>Methodology</h2>
        </div>
        <ul class="content-list">
          <li>Open corpora only, including FiQA and MSMARCO.</li>
          <li>No synthetic data in the published benchmark runs.</li>
          <li>Contributions and issue reports live in the public repo.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="panel">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <h2>Links</h2>
      </div>
      <ul class="content-list">
        <li><a class="inline-link" href="https://quaid.app">quaid.app</a></li>
        <li><a class="inline-link" href="https://github.com/quaid-app/quaid-evals">github.com/quaid-app/quaid-evals</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
